    {
        "content": "<p>Hmm... it seems to me that Lean does not like <em>hiding</em> the variable <code>n</code> in <code>V</code>. <br>\nFor now, I'll just stick to using <code>(n ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ)</code> everywhere. <br>\nI'm a bit sad though that there is no straightforward way in Lean to simply rename a term like <code>(n ‚Üí ‚ÑÇ)</code></p>",
