    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"bp\">@</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">derive</span> <span class=\"n\">add_comm_group</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">derive</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">vector_space</span> <span class=\"n\">‚ÑÇ</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"n\">derive</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">finite_dimensional</span> <span class=\"n\">‚ÑÇ</span><span class=\"o\">)]</span>\n<span class=\"n\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">V</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span> <span class=\"n\">u</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">fintype</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">n</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚Üí</span> <span class=\"n\">‚ÑÇ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n\n<p>I don't know if it's possible to get <code>[fintype n]</code> on only the <code>finite_dimensional</code> instance</p>",
